Friday May 27

Beach Day and Catamaran Ride

Free Time

Today we will be enjoying the beaches of Sitges and generally relaxing and getting things ready for the event tomorrow.

If you would like to explore feel free to do so! Barcelona is a short drive away, and there are plenty of activities around Sitges as well.

Catamaran Ride

This evening close to sunset we will be taking a Catamran ride into the Mediterranian. Bring your suits and look forward to exploring the wonderful blue waters

Barbeque

We will be having an evening BBQ at the Can Marcer tonight to relax and enjoy everyones company before the event tomorrow!

); }; export default Day27;
